OL,3,CPopular theme park to permanently
OL,4,Cclose as costs rise and visitors
OL,5,Cdwindle
OL,7,FA popular Cornish theme park has
OL,8,Fannounced it will close "with
OL,9,Fimmediate effect" due to rising
OL,10,Foperating costs and dwindling visitor
OL,11,Fnumbers.
OL,13,FThe owners of Flambards Theme Park in
OL,14,FHelston said they had taken the
OL,15,Fdecision only after "all possible
OL,16,Favenues had been exhausted".
OL,18,FThey added that the closure would not
OL,19,Faffect the Masked Ball on Saturday 9
OL,20,FNovember, which is going ahead as
OL,21,Fplanned.
