OL,7,FSeveral older rides ceased operating
OL,8,Fthis year, due to the difficulty in
OL,9,Ffinding "specialised parts" and
OL,10,Fsomeone able to maintain them, the
OL,11,Fpark's statement said.
OL,13,FIt continued: "Additionally, the much-
OL,14,Floved Victorian Village exhibition now
OL,15,Frequires extensive remedial work; it
OL,16,Fwill remain closed while we
OL,17,Finvestigate alternative options to
OL,18,Fpreserve and honour this unique
OL,19,Fcollection.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
