OL,5,Cdwindle
OL,7,F"While the theme park itself will no
OL,8,Flonger operate, we can confirm Ferdi's
OL,9,FFunland, the indoor play centre, will
OL,10,Fre-open as a standalone attraction on
OL,11,FNovember 17th, providing a familiar
OL,12,Fplace of play for younger visitors.
OL,14,F"Flambards has been a cherished
OL,15,Fdestination for generations, and it is
OL,16,Fwith a heavy heart that we bid
OL,17,Ffarewell.
