OL,7,F"To our loyal supporters and dedicated
OL,8,Fteam, who have given their unwavering
OL,9,Fcommitment through difficult times, we
OL,10,Fextend our sincerest gratitude.
OL,12,F"Thank you for making Flambards a
OL,13,Fspecial place."
OL,15,FThe park also posted the statement on
OL,16,FFacebook and people were quick to
OL,17,Fcomment with their reactions.
