OL,7,FOne said: "So sad, I remember
OL,8,Fcollecting the coupons out of the
OL,9,FCornishman so my children could have a
OL,10,FSeason Ticket to go whenever they
OL,11,Fliked with their friends all through
OL,12,Fthe School holidays.
OL,14,F"They all thought they were so grown
OL,15,Fup catching the bus from Penzance
OL,16,Ftogether. Fond memories, thank you
OL,17,FFlambards and best of luck to all the
OL,18,Fstaff."
